episodes.title: New docuseries 'Cult Massacre: One Day in Jonestown'
episodes.description: A new three-part docuseries called Cult Massacre: One Day in Jonestown is now streaming. Using a wealth of footage filmed in the days before, during, and after the massacre -- it brings the tragedy that left more than 900 people dead to a whole new audience. Laura Spence, a producer on the project, joined Angela to share more about the new series.
